  "body": "- [ ] I've asked for help in the [Truffle Gitter](http://gitter.im/Consensys/truffle) before filing this issue.\r\n\r\n---------------------------\r\n\r\n## Issue\r\n`Truffle init` on a computer without wifi throws unhandled error\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\nTurn off wifi, `truffle init`\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nSome kind of message that indicates truffle needs internet to run this command\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n\r\n```\r\nevents.js:163\r\n      throw er; // Unhandled 'error' event\r\n      ^\r\n\r\nError: getaddrinfo EAI_AGAIN raw.githubusercontent.com:443\r\n    at Object.exports._errnoException (util.js:1050:11)\r\n    at errnoException (dns.js:33:15)\r\n    at GetAddrInfoReqWrap.onlookup [as oncomplete] (dns.js:73:26)\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System:  Tried on windows 10 and ubuntu 16.04, same behaviour\r\n* Truffle version: Truffle v3.4.9 (core: 3.4.8)\r\n* Ethereum client: n/a\r\n* node version: v7.10.1\r\n* npm version: 5.4.2\r\n",
